<h1>GoC Web Template Samples - Sign In Example</h1>
<p><a href="http://www.gcpedia.gc.ca/wiki/Content_Delivery_Network/GoC_.NET_template_guide">Web Template Documentation (GCPedia)</a></p>
<p>The Sign In Button is available in the application template.</p>
<p><code class="wb-prettify">ShowSignInLink</code> is a boolean variable that is used to either show or hide the Sign In Button</p>
<p>
    <code class="wb-prettify">ShowSignInURL</code> is the location of your sign in page for this web application, this can also be set in the web.config.
    If this is set in the web.config it should navigate to a page that is hooked into the applications localization.
</p>
<div class="wb-prettify all-pre lang-vb linenums">
    .
    <h3>C# Code Sample</h3>
    <pre>WebTemplateCore.ShowSignInLink = true; //Show the sign in button
WebTemplateCore.SignInLinkURL = "about:blank"; //The URL to your applications sign in page.</pre>
</div>